Class Event3Distributor<T1,T2,T3>

  net.objectzoo.events.impl.Event3Distributor<T1,T2,T3>
Type Parameters:

T3 - The type of the third information parameter the event provides
All Implemented Interfaces:
Action3<T1,T2,T3>, Event3<T1,T2,T3>, Event3Delegate<T1,T2,T3>
public class Event3Distributor<T1,T2,T3>
extends Object
implements Event3Delegate<T1,T2,T3>

The Event3Distributor is a Event3Delegate implementation that allows event distribution to multiple subscribers. It is a helper class that encapsulates all the logic required to provide events in other classes. Subscriber invocations are performed in the order of subscription.

tilmann
